---
import PageLayout from "../../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto p-6 prose prose-invert">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      We do not actively collect personal information through this website. If you contact us via email or phone, we will retain the information you provide solely for the purpose of responding to your enquiry.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      Our admin panel (Decap CMS) uses cookies for authentication purposes. No other cookies are used on this site. You may disable cookies in your browser settings, though this may affect access to the admin area.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      This website links to third-party services including Google Maps, Instagram, Facebook, and delivery partners (Deliveroo, Uber Eats, Just Eat). These services have their own privacy policies governing how they handle your data. We encourage you to review them.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>
      Any personal information you provide via email or phone is retained only as long as necessary to address your enquiry. We do not sell, share, or otherwise distribute your personal information.
    </p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
      Under UK data protection law, you have the right to request access to any personal data we may hold about you, and to request its deletion. To make such a request, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.
    </p>
  </main>
</PageLayout>
